title: The Groom Drank So Much At His Wedding Because He Didn't Want To Be There!
description:
One of Moe's good friend almost ruined his entire wedding after he indulged in the alcohol a LITTLE too much. When Moe jokingly asked him if it was because he didn’t want to be married, his answer was shocking!
